						               													<description>User summary:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A space-ship themed cooperative game. Players are crew on a derelict spaceship that has wandered in in a dangerous space zone. Game is played on the board that represent the space ship, with various stations such as the bridge, engine room, resting room and so on. On their turn, players roll a die to see what threat happens (ship breaks down, asteroids or space slime attacks), then may do one movement and one action; action depending on what station the player is &amp;ndash; an action in the sensor room will increase the sensor system, an action on the bridge will navigate the ship.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All character have different stats in various actions, repairing, and endurance points, that may be used to strain the character for extra actions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to increase the sensor system enough so that the players manage to navigate out of the dangerous zone. Game is lost if any player dies, if the spaceship collides with an asteroid or if too many space jellyfish cling to the hull.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
